dc_description_s: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Published under the direction of Colonel C.A.K. Wilson, O.B.E., F.R.I.C.S., Surveyor General of Pākistān. Corrected up to 1950." "1st edition 1929; 2nd (revised)1940; 3rd edition 1944; 4th (revised) 1951." Ancillary map: Index to bus routes & tramways. Scale 1" = 1 mile. On verso: legend and reference list, and index to sources of map. "Reg. No. 1199 M.D'50(D.O.I-3".6)5000'51-1000'57." Copy two: "Reg. No. 1199 M.D'50(D.O.I-3".6)5000'51-1000'58." Map collection has two copies. Both are kept.
